  "texts": [
    "BACKGROUND A. LLM ChatbotAn LLM chatbot is a conversational agent that integrates an LLM as backend.",
    "Such a chatbot service, which can be accessed through various interfaces such as web platforms or APIs, is capable of generating human-like responses and creative content, and respond to various content.",
    "Examples of chatbots include ChatGPT from OpenAI, Bard from Google, and Claude [3].",
    "They significantly improve the users' experience and efficiency, with the potential of revolutionizing various industries.It is important for LLM chatbot service providers to set forth some ethical guidelines.",
    "The aim of these guidelines is to ensure responsible utilization of their services, curbing the generation of content that is violent or of a sensitive nature."
  ],
